@startuml
title MQTT to Kuksa Databroker Workflow

actor "Driver" as Driver
participant "Joystick ECU\n(Arduino)" as ECU
participant "Mosquitto\n(MQTT Broker)" as Broker
participant "MQTT-to-gRPC Bridge" as Bridge
participant "Kuksa Databroker" as Kuksa
participant "CAN Provider" as CAN

Driver -> ECU: Move joystick / press button
ECU -> Broker: Publish JSON on InVehicleTopics
Broker -> Bridge: Deliver MQTT message
Bridge -> Kuksa: gRPC Val/Set updates
Kuksa -> CAN: Target value updates
CAN -> ECU: CAN frames to blinker ECU

@enduml
